data.description: Welcome home! This single story Corona dream features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 car attached garage, upgraded kitchen with granite counters and upgraded cabinets, wood and carpet flooring in living space, tile flooring in bathrooms, newer interior paint, in ground spa, covered patio, deck, pristine landscaping, fantastic neighborhood, and so much more! Hurry this will not last!!!
data.whatILove: Beautiful professional landscaping, large mature trees, stamped concrete, recently remodeled kitchen and bathrooms, close proximity to schools and shopping, nearby park, quiet and friendly neighborhood, beautiful and relaxing backyard, easy access to I-15 and 91 freeways.
